snippet.title: Johnny Depp's Shocking Revelations in Libel Trial
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp is suing "The Sun" for allegations he abused his ex, Amber Heard. In court, Depp admitted to spending $30,000 a month on wine and drugs but said it never resulted in abuse towards his ex.
